<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FC - SIGN IN</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/transition.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" href="img/FCLOGO4.png" type="image/png">
  <script src= "JS/showpassjs.js"> </script>
</head>

<body>

  <div class = "transition transition-1 is-active"> </div>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="LoggedInUpdate" class = "headbutt">UPDATES</a></li>
        <li><a href="LoggedIn" class = "headbutt">ABOUT</a></li>
        <li><a href="LoggedInReviews" class = "headbutt">REVIEWS</a></li>
        <li><a href="Game.html" class = "headbutt">GAME</a></li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
        <li><a class = "headbutt"><%= LoggedInUser.UserName %></a></li>
        <li><a href="Index" class = "headbutt">LogOut</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main id="mainmain">
    <div class="logobobo">
      <img src="http://localhost:3000/img/PEAR.png" alt="PEAR" width="224" height="335" id="pear">
      <img src="img/fruitclick1.png" alt="FRUIT CLICKER" width="1124" height="317" id="fruitclickername">
      <img src="img/BANANA.png" alt="BANANA" width="425" height="274" id="banana">
    </div>
    <div class="ptext">
      <p>Fruit Clicker is a clicker genre game that's available to everyone!</p>
      <p>Fruit Clicker does not require high concentration from the player and does not cause stress.</p>
      <p>This is the BEST game to play after a hard day. It is relaxing and entertaining!</p>
      <p>Trust me - you have never played such an interesting and exciting game before! DOWNLOAD NOW!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fatab">
      <div class="applesection">
        <img src="img/APPLE.png" alt="APPLE" width="234" height="292" id="apple">
        <p> In Fruit Clicker, all you
          have to do is to
          click on a tree and
          gain fruits </p>
      </div>
      <div class="moneysection">
        <img src="img/MONEY.png" alt="MONEY" width="326" height="277" id="money">
        <p> You can sell the
          harvested fruits
          for in-game
          currency. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="upgradesection">
        <img src="img/UPGRADE.png" alt="UPGRADE" width="580" height="191" id="upgrade">
        <p>
          For game currency, you
          can buy various upgrades
          to speed up your progress
          and get even more fruits!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <div class="footero">
      <a> FruitClick.inc </a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>